data.description: Quiet culdesac with great curb appeal. Previous model home. Exterior paint & new roof installed in 2015, new vinyl windows, new porcelain tile flooring downstairs in main traffic areas. New triple pane vinyl windows. Kitchen has granite counters, beautiful center island, stainless steel appliances, trash pullout cabinet; refrigerator & washer/dryer included. 3 car garage, RV pad & outside storage shed. Mature landscaping w/ fruit trees, front yard water feature & exterior landscape lights in front walkway. Upstairs primary bathroom has been recently updated. Wood burning fireplace, Garage has insulated garage doors lots of storage/cabinets. Open house - champagne tour this Saturday 10/21/22 from 1pm to 4pm!
